==English==
===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''the Ionian Islands'''

#A group of [[island]]s in the [[Ionian Sea]] - one of the 13 [[peripheries]] of [[Greece]]  The main islands are [[Corfu]], [[Ithaca]], [[Kefallonia]], [[Kythira]], [[Lefkada]], [[Paxoi]] and [[Zante]].

